## Banned Defaults

Do not use any of these without explicitly naming why and getting approval:

- `bg-white` or `background: white` as a page background
- Tailwind blue (`blue-500`, `blue-600`) as primary action color
- `rounded-full` on rectangular buttons
- Box shadows from Tailwind defaults (`shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`)
- `transition: all`
- Equal-column CSS grid as default layout
- Identical internal structure for different card types
- `from-blue-500 to-purple-600` gradients
- Hero section with H1 + subheading + two buttons + hero image (the template)
- Navbar with logo left, links right, CTA button — without any typographic
  or motion treatment that makes it feel designed
- Footer as a dark box with 4 link columns

