## Hard Constraints (Immutable)

When the user says "do not change" a value, it is locked permanently.
Do not override, suggest alternatives, or deviate under any circumstance.

- **Accent color:** `#c8a97e` (warm aged amber) — never green, never blue
- **Animation library:** `gsap@3.12.5` only — no framer-motion, no AOS, no anime.js
- **Noise library:** `simplex-noise@4.0.3` only
- **Fonts:** Archivo, DM Mono, Instrument Serif — no substitutions
- **Build cadence:** one isolated piece at a time — wait for approval before adding anything new
- **No unsolicited packages or files**